{{National football association | Logo = Cape Verde FA.png | Founded = 1982 | FIFA affiliation = 1986 | Region = [[Confederation of African Football|CAF]] | Region affiliation = 2000 | President = Victor Osório | Coach = [[José Rui]] | }}
The '''Cape Verdean Football Federation''' ({{lang-pt|Federação Caboverdiana de Futebol, FCF}}) is the governing body of [[Football (soccer)|football]] in [[Cape Verde]]. It was founded in 1982, affiliated to [[FIFA]] in 1986 and to [[Confederation of African Football|CAF]] in 2000. It organizes the national football league and the [[Cape Verde national football team|national team]].<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/jan/28/air-traffic-controller-cape-verde |title=Air traffic controller directs Cape Verde football team to sporting glory &#124; Football |publisher=The Guardian |date= |accessdate=2013-08-15}}</ref>
Its current president is Victor Osório since 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oceanpress.info/index.php/Pt/desporto/item/22398-victor-osorio-toma-posse-como-presidente-da-fcf|title=Victor Osório toma posse como Presidente da FCF|newspaper=[[Oceanpress]]|language=pt|date=17 April 2015|accessdate=20 April 2015}}</ref>
The federation is headquartered in the capital city of [[Praia]] and is located on Avenida Cidade de Lisboa in the subdivision of [[Várzea, Praia|Várzea]] where the sport complexes are located.
Is offices is just south of [[Estádio da Várzea]] and features a small field on the east part. The building was completed in 2006 after the nearby stadium was also repaired. Since 2013, the Caixa building is adjacent to its offices.
==Premier League or Interisland league== {{Unreferenced section|date=July 2010}} {{Main|Cape Verdean football Championships}}
The Capeverdean Premier division are made up of two groups, Groups A and B and the team with the most points in the island but Santiago and Santo Antão are divided into two zones in the island qualifies into the premier division and not the top teams from the second or third divisions in other places. There are only about five to six rounds becore heading to the playoffs and are played in the months of May or June.
The premier league as well as the island divisions has several teams, more teams can be seen at another title below this one:
