{{Unreferenced|date=August 2007}}'''Rafik Sorman Stadium''' ({{lang-ar|ستاد رفيق سورمان}}) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Sorman]], [[Libya]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Rafik Sorman]].  The stadium holds 8,000 people.

