{{infobox country at games|NOC=SWE|NOCname=[[Swedish Olympic Committee]]|games=Summer Universiade|year=2017|date=July 19-30|flagcaption=|oldcode=|website=|location=[[Taipei]]|competitors=68 (32 men & 36 women)|sports=12|flagbearer=|rank=|gold=0|silver=1|bronze=1|officials=|appearances=|seealso=}}
'''[[Sweden]]''' participated at the [[2017 Summer Universiade]] which was held in [[Taipei]], [[Taiwan]].
Sweden sent a delegation consisting of 68 competitors for the event competing in 12 sporting events.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://data.2017.gov.taipei/atos/prod/eng/zz/engzz_general-nusf-overview-Sweden-.htm|title=Taipei 2017 Summer Universiade NUSF Overview Sweden|website=data.2017.gov.taipei|access-date=2017-12-28}}</ref>Sweden claimed two medals at the multi-sport event.
