{{infobox country at games | NOC = THA | NOCname = [[National Olympic Committee of Thailand]] | games = Summer Olympics | year = 1984 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.olympicthai.or.th }}&nbsp;{{th icon}} {{en icon}} | location = [[Los Angeles, California|Los Angeles]] | competitors = 39 | sports = 5 | flagbearer = [[Rangsit Yanothai]] | rank = 33 | gold = 0 | silver = 1 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }}
'''[[Thailand]]''' competed at the '''[[1984 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Los Angeles, California|Los Angeles]], [[United States]]. The nation returned to the Summer Games after participating in the [[American-led boycott of the 1980 Summer Olympics]].
==Medalists==
===Silver=== * [[Dhawee Umponmaha]] &mdash; [[Boxing at the 1984 Summer Olympics|Boxing]], Men's Light Welterweight
==Results by event==
