;Men's Individual Competition * [[Amphol Amalekajorn]] &ndash; 2342 points (→ 46th place) * [[Wachera Piyapattra]] &ndash; 2328 points (→ 50th place)
===Athletics=== {{main|Athletics at the 1984 Summer Olympics}}
'''Women's 100 metres''' * [[Wallapa Tangjitnusom]] :* First Heat &mdash; 12.18s (→ did not advance)
'''Women's Long Jump''' *[[Sarinee Phenglaor]] :* Qualification &mdash; 5.51 m (→ did not advance, 22nd place)
===Boxing=== {{main|Boxing at the 1984 Summer Olympics}}
;Men's Light Flyweight (&ndash;48&nbsp;kg) * [[Sanpol Sang-Ano]] *# First round &ndash; lost to {{flagIOCathlete|[[Daniel Mwangi (boxer)|Daniel Mwangi]]|KEN|1984 Summer}}, RSC-3
;Men's Bantamweight (54&nbsp;kg) *[[Wanchai Pongsri]] *# First round &ndash; bye *# Second round &ndash; lost to {{flagIOCathlete|[[Joe Orewa]]|NIG|1984 Summer}}, KO-2
