{{Infobox stadium | name = Yunost Stadium | image = | location = [[Mozyr]], [[Belarus]] | coordinates = {{Coord|52|2|20|N|29|16|37.5|E|display=inline|type:landmark}} | built = | opened = 1991 | renovated = | expanded = | closed = | surface = Grass | former_names = | tenants = [[FC Slavia-Mozyr|Slavia-Mozyr]] | capacity = 5,133 | dimensions = 105 x 68 metres }} '''Yunost Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Mozyr]], [[Belarus]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[FC Slavia-Mozyr|Slavia-Mozyr]]. The stadium was opened in 1992 and currently holds 5,133 people.<ref>[http://www.pressball.by/footballstat/stadiums/11/ Stadium information]</ref>
